title: Delicious Parisian Quiche ! feat. the Vagabrothers
description:
Taste of Paris ! Video recipe on how to make a Parisian Quiche, using ingredients you can find everywhere. Asparagus, Ham, Button mushrooms and most of all a home made crust, crispy and buttery and crumbly crust. You're gonna get crazy for it.

In this video I am joined by my friends the Vagabrothers. They travel all around and share their best tips and tricks on their youtube channel ! Check them out here :
http://www.youtube.com/vagabrothers

A quiche is a pie, filled with a savory custard. It's made with eggs, milk, cream and butter. It's flavored with pepper, and nutmeg. Quiche lorraine is the classic one, but in this video I am showing you how to make a Parisian Twist on this classic pie.
